  {"qe":"Kautilya's Arthashastra mainly deals with?","qh":"कौटिल्य का अर्थशास्त्र मुख्यतः किससे संबंधित है?","opts":["Philosophy","Economics and statecraft","Religion","Literature"],"ans":1,"exp":"Arthashastra by Kautilya (Chanakya) is an ancient treatise on statecraft, economic policy and military strategy.","diff":"medium"},
  {"qe":"The Swadeshi Movement started after?","qh":"स्वदेशी आंदोलन किसके बाद शुरू हुआ?","opts":["Non-Cooperation Movement","Partition of Bengal (1905)","Salt Satyagraha","Simon Commission visit"],"ans":1,"exp":"Swadeshi Movement (1905) started in response to Lord Curzon's Partition of Bengal.","diff":"medium"},
