  {"qe":"The Black Soil (Regur) is best for which crop?","qh":"काली मिट्टी किस फसल के लिए सर्वोत्तम है?","opts":["Rice","Wheat","Cotton","Sugarcane"],"ans":2,"exp":"Black cotton soil (Regur) is ideal for cotton cultivation — found in Deccan Plateau (Maharashtra, Gujarat).","diff":"medium"},
