  {"qe":"Roaring Forties, Furious Fifties, Screaming Sixties are related to?","qh":"Roaring Forties किससे संबंधित हैं?","opts":["Ocean currents","Persistent westerly winds in Southern Ocean","Types of clouds","Storm systems"],"ans":1,"exp":"Roaring Forties (40°S), Furious Fifties (50°S) and Screaming Sixties (60°S) are powerful westerly winds.","diff":"hard"},
  {"qe":"The Greenwich Meridian (0°) passes through which of these Indian states?","qh":"ग्रीनविच मध्याह्न रेखा भारत से गुजरती है?","opts":["Yes, through Rajasthan","Yes, through Gujarat","No, not through India","Yes, through Maharashtra"],"ans":2,"exp":"Greenwich Meridian (0° longitude) does not pass through India. India is between 68°E and 97°E.","diff":"medium"},
