  {"qe":"The Monsoon in India originates from?","qh":"भारत में मानसून कहाँ से आता है?","opts":["Bay of Bengal only","Arabian Sea only","Both Arabian Sea and Bay of Bengal","Indian Ocean only"],"ans":2,"exp":"Indian Monsoon has two branches: Arabian Sea branch (SW monsoon) and Bay of Bengal branch.","diff":"medium"},
