  {"qe":"The highest plateau in the world is?","qh":"विश्व का सबसे ऊँचा पठार?","opts":["Deccan Plateau","Colorado Plateau","Tibetan Plateau (Pamir)","Brazilian Plateau"],"ans":2,"exp":"Tibetan Plateau (Roof of the World) at avg 4,500m is the world's highest and largest plateau.","diff":"medium"},
